CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of nine men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence signing document, P. L. Prattis seated on right, and another on right wearing clerical collar, and three women, gathered around oval table in the Office of the Mayor, City County Building
